 * Camphora Five.
 */
app:camphora-five
  name:Camphora 7.0
  description:Create data driven CRUD apps without coding, and import/export data to and from Excel etc
  url:"https://phosphorusfive.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/camphora-five2.zip"
  price:Free
  local-url:camphora-five
  image:"https://phosphorusfive.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/legos-hero.png"
  developer-key:5E11AEF421CDB0A7A9A5C6B4AED9D04F43BE2AAD
  condition:p5.io.unroll-path.@CAMPHORA
  version:decimal:6.3
    event:camphora.version
  author-readme:@"Camphora Five allows you to rapidly create data driven web applications, without needing to code. It allows you to create CRUD apps declaratively. Examples of use cases can be found beneath.

* Put your Excel files online
* Create rich form web applications
* C.R.U.D - Create, Read, Update and Delete

Basically, Camphora Five allows you to create a data driven app, which you can use to collect, edit, read and delete data, using any internet capable device you wish. It stores its data in a generically created MySQL database."





