  condition:p5.io.unroll-path.@HYPER-CORE
  version:decimal:7.0
    event:hyper-core.version
  author-readme:@"Hyper Core is a generic back for your JavaScript based front end web apps, and contains among other things, a REST based ORM library for MySQL. It is extendible in nature, and can easily wrap any other database you want to use, or any server side business logic object for that matter.

It allows you to easily control access to your back end REST based web service endpoints, by creating access objects, allowing you to fine grain access, to roles and users of your systems, to specific operations you want to allow or deny, according to roles."





